                            oc:tableCaption "## Parameters Tuning" ;
                            oc:tableMarkdown """| Parameter | Lower Value | Higher Value |
|-----------|-------------|--------------|
| `threshold_ratio` | More aggressive | More conservative |
| `min_duration` | Shorter pauses | Longer pauses only |
